",null,{}]]}],\\\"Celebrates Nigeria’s independence with participants mimicking nationalist dress and receiving handmade Nigerian flags.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold text-primary font-montserrat\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Digital Resources:\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",null,{}]]}],\\\"NML provides online access to parts of their collections, virtual tours, educational materials, and digital exhibitions, allowing broader access to their resources.\\\"]}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-[100%] font-old  text-[0.75rem] sm:text-[16px] sm:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-6 font-light w-full  border-black p-8\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"NML provides online access to parts of their collections, virtual tours, educational materials, and digital exhibitions, allowing broader access to their resources.\\\"]}],\\\"$L13\\\",\\\"$L14\\\",\\\"$L15\\\",\\\"$L16\\\"]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"a:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"w-[100%] h-[100%] font-montserrat flex justify-between bg-background border-primary border-x-[1px] flex-col sm:flex-row columns-2 overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-[100%] font-old  text-[0.75rem] sm:text-[16px] sm:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-6 font-light w-full  border-black p-8\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold text-primary font-montserrat\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Public Events:\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",null,{}]]}],\\\"MNL host a variety of public events, including lectures, panel discussions and cultural performances, which are often related to current exhibitions or broader cultural topics.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold text-primar